data.description: Welcome home to city living at it's best! Relax and enjoy the front porch with a view of the park.  This home is newly renovated throughout, and features 3 bedrooms, 1st floor powder room and a finished basement with walkout. There are two garages with electricity, and a 2nd floor.  The kitchen features all new energy efficient stainless appliances including a dishwasher. This home has a new roof, newer heating system and is also equipped with new central air for those hot summer days. Everything has been done, just move right in and enjoy.
